<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>英语-VICE</title><link>https://www.vice.com/en/</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Mon, 30 Mar 2026 01:17:48 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>LL Cool J 曾解释为什么他在职业生涯几十年后仍然从事音乐事业：“我进入嘻哈音乐并不是为了钱”</title><link>https://www.vice.com/en/article/ll-cool-j-once-explained-why-he-still-makes-music-decades-into-his-career-i-didnt-get-into-hip-hop-for-money/</link><description>&lt;p&gt;LL Cool J 在 2008 年解释了为什么他仍然创作音乐，尽管他并不需要这样做，并指出金钱从来不是他职业生涯的一个因素。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.vice.com/en/article/ll-cool-j-once-explained-why-he-still-makes-music-decades-into-his-career-i-didnt-get-into-hip-hop-for-money/"&gt;LL Cool J 曾经解释过为什么他几十年来仍将音乐融入自己的职业生涯：“我进入嘻哈音乐并不是为了钱”，&lt;/a&gt;该帖子首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.vice.com"&gt;VICE&lt;/a&gt;上。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Sun, 29 Mar 2026 18:40:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.vice.com/en/article/ll-cool-j-once-explained-why-he-still-makes-music-decades-into-his-career-i-didnt-get-into-hip-hop-for-money/</guid></item><item><title>OJ Da Juiceman 在警方拘留期间被紧急送往医院接受医疗急救</title><link>https://www.vice.com/en/article/oj-da-juiceman-rushed-to-the-hospital-for-medical-emergency-while-in-police-custody/</link><description>&lt;p&gt;OJ Da Juiceman 患有糖尿病多年，目前因涉嫌与州警发生冲突而被警方拘留。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.vice.com/en/article/oj-da-juiceman-rushed-to-the-hospital-for-medical-emergency-while-in-police-custody/"&gt;OJ Da Juiceman 在警察拘留期间因医疗紧急情况被送往医院的&lt;/a&gt;帖子首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.vice.com"&gt;VICE&lt;/a&gt;上。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Sun, 29 Mar 2026 17:06:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.vice.com/en/article/oj-da-juiceman-rushed-to-the-hospital-for-medical-emergency-while-in-police-custody/</guid></item><item><title>比莉·艾利什的跟踪者在突发火车事故中丧生</title><link>https://www.vice.com/en/article/billie-eilishs-stalker-killed-in-sudden-train-accident/</link><description>&lt;p&gt;普雷内尔·卢梭（Prenell Rousseau）曾跟踪比莉·艾利什（Billie Eilish）及其家人，现已在长岛被火车撞死。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.vice.com/en/article/billie-eilishs-stalker-killed-in-sudden-train-accident/"&gt;比莉·艾利什 (Billie Eilish) 的跟踪者在火车突发事故中身亡的&lt;/a&gt;帖子首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.vice.com"&gt;VICE&lt;/a&gt;上。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Sun, 29 Mar 2026 16:00:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.vice.com/en/article/billie-eilishs-stalker-killed-in-sudden-train-accident/</guid></item><item><title>Questlove 回忆起必须向父母隐瞒自己对嘻哈音乐的根源和热爱的经历</title><link>https://www.vice.com/en/article/questlove-recalls-having-to-hide-the-roots-and-his-love-for-hip-hop-from-his-parents/</link><description>&lt;p&gt;Questlove 回忆起他不得不隐瞒自己和父亲一起在 The Roots 的事实，因为他知道父亲不赞成嘻哈音乐。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.vice.com/en/article/questlove-recalls-having-to-hide-the-roots-and-his-love-for-hip-hop-from-his-parents/"&gt;Questlove 回忆起必须向父母隐藏根源以及他对嘻哈音乐的热爱的&lt;/a&gt;帖子首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.vice.com"&gt;VICE&lt;/a&gt;上。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Sun, 29 Mar 2026 14:20:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.vice.com/en/article/questlove-recalls-having-to-hide-the-roots-and-his-love-for-hip-hop-from-his-parents/</guid></item><item><title>贝塞斯达将其最具争议的《上古卷轴》游戏下线</title><link>https://www.vice.com/en/article/bethesda-is-taking-its-most-controversial-elder-scrolls-game-offline/</link><description>&lt;p&gt;Bethesda 确认，一款《上古卷轴》游戏将在 7 年后于 2026 年 6 月 30 日结束。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.vice.com/en/article/bethesda-is-taking-its-most-controversial-elder-scrolls-game-offline/"&gt;贝塞斯达将其最具争议的《上古卷轴》游戏下线的&lt;/a&gt;帖子首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.vice.com"&gt;VICE&lt;/a&gt;上。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Sun, 29 Mar 2026 13:43:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.vice.com/en/article/bethesda-is-taking-its-most-controversial-elder-scrolls-game-offline/</guid></item><ite